
SaferD:

Usage: saferd [dir1] [dir2] ... 

Monitor [dirs] for changes. Upon changes call the below shell script hooks:

In Directory "hooks":
	DirCreated.sh  DirDeleted.sh  FileCreated.sh  FileDeleted.sh

Each file can be scripted in shell script to manipulate the system based
upon the change to any files in followed paths.

Run the program from the current working directory. All modified and created
files will be created in this working directory.

Author:
	
Al Poole <al.poole@outlook.com>
